thread.title: Re: Report: Object throw at Trump motorcade in Florida
thread.title_full: Re: Report: Object throw at Trump motorcade in Florida

author: Duane Savage
title: Re: Report: Object throw at Trump motorcade in Florida
text:
Report: Object thrown at Trump motorcade in Florida Posted at 7:01 pm on February 17, 2017 by William A. 
The Secret Service is investigating after an object of some sort with thrown at President Trump’s motorcade while it was leaving the airport in Palm Beach, FL: Secret Service is investigating incident in which an object was thrown at Trump's motorcade https://t.co/VptGV4Ailv https://t.co/MjjIujYOcX 
— CNN International (@cnni) February 17, 2017 NEW: Secret Service source says it's investigating an object thrown at Pres Trump's motorcade on his arrival in West Palm Beach. 
— Peter Alexander (@PeterAlexander) February 17, 2017 
The object was possibly a “baseball sized rock”: Secret Service investigating object thrown at Trump's motorcade, baseball sized rock found near scene https://t.co/wBY4H1s5Pq 
— Jeffrey Guterman (@JeffreyGuterman) February 17, 2017 More: The presidential limo was not hit by the object, apparently a rock, senior law enforcement official tells @ABC News. (2/2) 
— ABC News (@ABC) February 17, 2017 Secret Service investigating after vehicle hit by object thrown at Pres. Trump's motorcade in south Florida – @kristindonnelly 
— NBC Nightly News (@NBCNightlyNews) February 17, 2017 Trending
